title: The Complete Asian Cookbook - Srilanka & The Philippines - C
description:
Since its release in 1976, Charmaine Solomon's The Complete Asian Cookbook has become a culinary classic, introducing Asian cooking to more than a million readers worldwide and garnering a dedicated following around the globe.

The recipes from Sri Lanka and The Philippines are now available in this single volume.

Join Charmaine Solomon on a journey through Sri Lanka and The Philippines, celebrating the multicultural influences on the cookery of these countries. From Sri Lanka's spicy Tamil flavours and coastal seafood curries, to the expansive cuisine of The Philippines, which draws on Malay, Chinese and Spanish heritage, these diverse dishes will delight and inspire a new generation of cooks.
